  rangeOfMeaning:["ritually defiled","morally defiled","unclean spirits"],
  cultural:"Lev 11-15 catalogs sources of uncleanness. Edersheim describes Second-Temple purity codes in daily life.",
  kingdomSignificance:"The kingdom's invitation reaches the unclean and cleanses them.",
  relatedVerses:["Leviticus 11-15","Isaiah 6:5","Isaiah 64:6","Haggai 2:13","Mark 1:23-27","Mark 1:40-45","Mark 5:1-20, 25-34","Acts 10:14-15","Romans 14:14","2 Corinthians 6:17","Ephesians 5:5","Revelation 17:4","Revelation 21:27"],
